- `context.ReportDiagnostic`: Allows you to report diagnostic messages (warnings or errors) during the source generation process.

By leveraging the `GeneratorExecutionContext`, you can perform various tasks related to code generation, including creating files in the output directory, analyzing the project's source code, and modifying the compilation output.

